{"tid":1535701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Sir, this way] 美軍首次與東盟在南海軍演","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:54:51.000Z","uid":171718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c20567af7e661cdb1f92e95950f88b75154f6743","tid":1535701,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/01/world/asia/asean-us-navy-south-china-sea.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fasean-us-navy-south-china-sea.html&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=225b1f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/01/world/asia/asean-us-navy-south-china-sea.html</a><br />\n<br />\n完全無新聞講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口交部又無打嘴炮 <br />\n完全無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0712477e7a8cb86006a0a61358a7bf89160f7797","tid":1535701,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center